Simple bash script to setup a NUT netclient config from scratch.
Assumptions are Ubuntu 14.04.1, and that the nut server has only one UPS attached and is accessible by an already configured nut user+pass.
Prompts for:-
Nut SERVER NAME (on the local network)
Nut UPS NAME (as configured on the nut server)
Nut servers MONITOR USER (as configured on the nut server)
Nut server monitor users PASSWORD (as configured on the nut server)
